node.text: A short film made by my boy @yungjalapeneaux along with @alexanderkreig @mattsbelldp  he spent an incredible amount of time on this and it came out a masterpiece. Credits to everyone who made this possible! @ian_moone_film @alanaduval @alexanderkreig @mattsbelldp  @canaanjfrederick @kayleejomakeup @blchance117 @ksquared5
